### Create a Product (POST Endpoint)

POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop X1",
  "price": 1500,
  "description": "High-performance laptop"
}

### Search Product by Name

GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/search?name=Laptop
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Paginated List of Products (First 5)

GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Content-Type: application/json

### Filter Products by Price Range ($1000 - $3000)

GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/filter?minPrice=1000&maxPrice=3000
Content-Type: application/json
